-- Croatia’s Tehnika Signs $21.7 Million Construction Contract
-- B y   J a s m i n a   K u z m a n o v i c
-- 2012-03-06T14:12:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/croatia-s-tehnika-signs-21-7-million-construction-contract.html
Croatia ’s largest construction
company  Tehnika d.d.  signed a 124.9 million-kuna ($21.7 million)
contract with the city of Zagreb to build an elementary school
and a kindergarten.  The project should be completed in 12 months, the Zagreb-
based company said in a statement to the  Zagreb bourse .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jasmina Kuzmanovic in Zagreb at 
